  removeToken(): void {
    localStorage.removeItem('jwtToken');
  }

}
```

In this code snippet, we have created an `AuthService` service that provides methods for setting, getting, and removing the JWT token from the local storage. This assertive approach ensures that the token is securely stored and easily accessible whenever needed.

